arm_group.description:
The patients in this arm of the study are healthy volunteers with no history of back pain in the last five years (see inclusion/exclusion criteria).
Propioception measures will be carried out in the following order:
Intervention: Calibration; Intervention: Practice; Intervention: Measures - no vibration; Intervention: Measures - high vibration; Intervention: Measures - low vibration;

